events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at Cleveland Cavaliers

headlines.description: — As a kid growing up in New York, Donovan Mitchell idolized LeBron James. On Tuesday night, he upstaged him.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mitchell upstages LeBron at home, Cavs down Lakers 116-102

headlines.description: — The Detroit Pistons had a rare easy win.
headlines.shortLinkText: Pistons run away in 2nd half, embarrass Heat 116-96

headlines.description: — Dorian Finney-Smith had someone in his ear after missing a late 3-pointer.
headlines.shortLinkText: Finney-Smith's late 3 helps Mavs to 116-115 win over Nuggets
